 schemes, C-RAN with\nhybrid RF/FSO fronthauling can achieve a considerable sum rate gain compared to\nconventional systems employing pure FSO fronthauling, especially under\nunfavorable atmospheric conditions. Moreover, employing a more sophisticated\nquantization scheme can significantly improve the system performance under\nadverse atmospheric conditions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Aug 2018 09:05:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-08-16"}
